# Terraform — never commit state (may contain sensitive values) or local caches
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.tfstate.lock.info
**/*.tfstate
**/*.tfstate.*
# Client-supplied inputs & secrets — never commit
**/terraform.tfvars
**/*.pem
# Keep the example and the provider lock
!**/terraform.tfvars.example
!**/.terraform.lock.hcl
